map j scroll up
map k scroll down
map d scroll half-down
map u scroll half-up

map J navigate previous
map K navigate next
map <S-Space> navigate previous
map <Space> navigate next

map [index] j navigate_index up
map [index] k navigate_index down

map <C-d> toggle_page_mode


